    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Magazines or books printed on cheap, low-quality paper made of wood pulp, which usually contain sensational material, such as lurid stories and articles. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
